    @58.Theattendantslistenedtoyourquestionsconcerns +
    @59.Theattendantsleftyoualoneforalongperiodoftime + @60.Overalltheattendantofferedcompassionatecare
    + @61.Theattendantshowedagenuineinterestinyourwellbeing + @62.Theattendantscoldedorshoutedatyou +
