COMPUTE EXPERIENCE=@65.Thinkingaboutyourexperiencehowlikelyareyoutorecommendthatpla +
    @66.Thinkingaboutyourexperiencesduringyourlastdeliveryhowlikelyw +
    @67.Thinkingaboutyourexperienceinthelastdeliveryhowlikelyareyout +
    @68.Thinkingaboutyourexperienceduringyourlastdeliveryhowlikelywo +
